                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>26th May 5624</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">If there are no<lb/> “Occident traces” in the printed off<lb/>\n                matter, we will not say anything<lb/> more of the few errors the Biography<lb/>\n                contained. But please look,<lb/> and <hi rend=\"underline\">let me know</hi>\n                whether<lb/> the Occident head lines have<lb/> indeed been retained. I need not<lb/>\n                ask you to be careful to remove<lb/> the traces in succeeding portions.<lb/> If 130\n                have been printed off<lb/> they will be enough.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As I am writing<lb/> hurriedly, I cannot stop to<lb/> recollect\n                where <add>לענים</add> occurs</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sb3xj8x/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
