                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>in the copy, nor did I know<lb/> that I omitted a letter in\n                shilling's<add>?</add>.<lb/> But nothing is more probable.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am sorry you took the<lb/> trouble to look up the queried<lb/>\n                word in the last copy in a Spanish<lb/> dictionary. The word being<lb/> Portuguese,\n                you would not<lb/> likely find it among Cathi<add>?</add><lb/>\n                <del>generally</del> gentry who are<lb/> proverbially exclusive.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I think it would<lb/> be better for you to address<lb/> the\n                    <persName>Benjamins</persName> direct—<lb/> Address <persName>Benjamin\n                    Bros</persName>—<lb/>\n                <placeName>Manchester</placeName>. If you like<lb/> however, as I correspond</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sb3xj8x/canvas/p2"
